STATE
v.
Carlos SEPULVEDA. No. 573P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. November 3, 2005. Joan M. Cunningham, Assistant Attorney General, Thomas J. Keith, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 3rd day of October 2005 by Defendant for Petition for Discretionary Review on Certification by Supreme Court Under G.S. 7A-31:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 3rd day of November 2005."
